provides inspiration for her cookbooks. In this ARTICLE, we=20
talk to Wells about French flavors and attitudes, and we ask=20
her to recommend some cookbooks that have an honored place in=20
her own kitchen. Try her recipe for GALLOPIN'S GREEN BEAN,=20
MUSHROOM, AND HAZELNUT SALAD from THE PARIS COOKBOOK.=20

