EATING, celebrity trainer Bob Greene offers in-depth nutrition=20
information and recipes that fit into his inspirational fitness=20
plan. He recommends positive lifestyle changes, not=20
get-thin-quick schemes, and he recognizes that enjoyment is an=20
important element of eating. Greene doesn't banish fat, which=20
adds flavor and creates a pleasant sense of satiety. Instead,=20
he includes fat in its most healthful forms.=20

