the quiet terror that permeated his The Sixth Sense, visionary=20
director M. Night Shyamalan presents the taut thriller SIGNS. Mel=20
Gibson plays a disillusioned priest who turns to farming and=20
discovers crop circles -- and then something much more ominous --=20
in his cornfields. Also starring Joaquin Phoenix and Rory Culkin.=20
The DVD includes five deleted scenes and an in-depth, six-part=20
documentary that explores the making of the movie.=20

Signs:
http://borders1.m0.net/m/s.asp?HB7922213127X1734034X151952X

